it is also possible to use formatting rules in comments. You can _underline_ your text or make it
*bold*. anything possible in articles, is possible in comments too.

CODE_START
#!/usr/bin/perl
use strict;

print "hello world\n .... BAZINGA!\n";
CODE_END

END_TEXT
